---
title: Bavette Steak & Creamy Horseradish Sauce  with Crispy Onion Petals, Fingerling Potatoes & Broccoli
description: The hottest ticket in town is your own dinner table! You’ll season and sizzle up juicy seasoned bavette steaks, while delicate tempura-battered onion petals fry to golden-brown perfection. Pair it all with roasted fingerling potatoes and broccoli, and drizzle with creamy horseradish sauce for a zippy, decadent finish.
